{
  "stem": "23131.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they lived on a lot of steps, and I couldn't walk up the steps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I called my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He ran to the drugstore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to call the-- the doctor to come because, you know, a little shtetl, and my father was so famous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I knew that she'll run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but I couldn't go on the steps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I climbed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I-- you know, I crawled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could not make one step.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally we got there and it was too late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As she walked out, as she was dressed, with her lipstick and with everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You would never say-- in fact, when we came home and he wanted to put her on the floor, I didn't let it because I said, look she's warm.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's-- she's alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you doing to her?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Help her.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Help her.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But don't-- don't put her on the floor because she's not dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, that's what had happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then my life started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was in 1938.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother was 47 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's when my Holo-- originally, my Holocaust started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- that was my 13th birthday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we had a very nice relationship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shivaed over me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- one girl and one boy, you know, and they wanted to raise us in the right way, with the traditional home, with the discipline, with the kavod.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, a-- a sort of shock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I personally never knew my mother's name, because they had such a name between them, between father and mother, that I never knew that my mother has a real name until-- you know, like, called Zina.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never knew because they had such a-- words between them-- such a-- no, what can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
